This paper proposes a deep learning method for shadow removal, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep networks for prediction, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions error reduction, which is a common evaluation metric in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper also deals with image processing, which falls under the scope of cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
